1
00:00:17,860 --> 00:00:21,760
♪Evening breeze cradles verdant hills♪

2
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:27,140
♪Embracing the waves of the deep sea♪

3
00:00:28,740 --> 00:00:33,670
♪Paper kites aim for distant shores♪

4
00:00:34,110 --> 00:00:37,400
♪Together, we conclude our tale♪

5
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:38,520
[Land of Dreams]

6
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:41,360
[Episode 13]

7
00:01:23,300 --> 00:01:24,660
Don't be afraid.

8
00:01:25,260 --> 00:01:28,340
Ms. Wu from next door
changed your clothes.

9
00:01:32,580 --> 00:01:34,540
Judging from the heat on my face,

10
00:01:34,860 --> 00:01:35,420
I can tell

11
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:37,660
your fever has gone down.

12
00:01:40,060 --> 00:01:40,980
It seems

13
00:01:41,900 --> 00:01:43,660
that I misunderstood you, Master.

14
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:45,700
But what is this place?

15
00:01:47,260 --> 00:01:48,260
It looks

16
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:50,180
like a woman's room.

17
00:01:51,180 --> 00:01:52,460
You took me here.

18
00:01:53,580 --> 00:01:55,900
Aren't you worried
the owner would get jealous?

19
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:03,420
This is my sister's room.

20
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:05,660
Don't mind it.

21
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:07,460
She doesn't want to come back here.

22
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:08,660
Besides,

23
00:02:09,220 --> 00:02:10,340
my sister

24
00:02:11,980 --> 00:02:13,180
is a generous person.

25
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:15,340
I don't think she will get jealous.

26
00:02:16,420 --> 00:02:19,060
Besides, if she liked me,

27
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:21,780
she wouldn't run away from home.

28
00:02:27,180 --> 00:02:28,500
How can you be sure

29
00:02:29,340 --> 00:02:30,420
that she doesn't like you?

30
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:34,060
What do you mean?

31
00:02:34,420 --> 00:02:35,740
Are you suggesting

32
00:02:37,260 --> 00:02:39,500
that my sister likes me?

33
00:02:43,060 --> 00:02:44,860
Oh, I'm so clueless.

34
00:02:46,260 --> 00:02:48,620
How could I not feel that?

35
00:02:51,140 --> 00:02:51,980
How about this?

36
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,540
I introduce the two of you
to each other.

37
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:56,220
Help me ask her someday.

38
00:03:02,380 --> 00:03:03,820
I don't think so.

39
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:07,340
Also,

40
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,820
if you like this place,

41
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:09,860
you can stay.

42
00:03:10,940 --> 00:03:11,460
What?

43
00:03:12,060 --> 00:03:12,820
You want me to stay?

44
00:03:13,180 --> 00:03:13,660
Yes.

45
00:03:22,140 --> 00:03:23,300
I prefer

46
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:25,740
to keep you around me.

47
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:32,580
Well, Master,

48
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:35,580
why do you have two faces?

49
00:03:36,100 --> 00:03:37,380
I also didn't expect

50
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:39,660
that my sister and disciple

51
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:41,500
have the same face.

52
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:44,820
♪Paper kites aim for distant shores♪

53
00:03:44,980 --> 00:03:48,580
♪Tasting the delights of the world♪

54
00:03:48,580 --> 00:03:49,700
Then, Master,

55
00:03:51,260 --> 00:03:53,180
do you prefer Guyu

56
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:55,140
or your sister?

57
00:03:56,020 --> 00:04:00,800
♪Shielding the tiles from wind and rain♪

58
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:04,060
♪Garments swept over the flowing water,
pristine and clean♪

59
00:04:04,060 --> 00:04:04,860
Get rest early.

60
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:12,260
♪Swinging through autumn
to Stone Bridge Bay♪

61
00:04:14,700 --> 00:04:19,140
♪In the land of dreams,
love sparks into wildfire♪

62
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:24,420
♪Radiant as the night sky,
setting the city aflame♪

63
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:27,760
♪Though trapped in deep mud,
I fear no changes♪

64
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:31,950
[Nanyan Residence]

65
00:04:58,220 --> 00:04:58,860
Master.

66
00:04:59,380 --> 00:05:00,300
May I touch

67
00:05:01,420 --> 00:05:02,260
this piano?

68
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:04,980
No.

69
00:05:06,460 --> 00:05:08,260
This is my sister's.

70
00:05:09,380 --> 00:05:12,500
I have promised her
that I won't let anyone touch it.

71
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:14,220
Do you keep all your promises

72
00:05:15,780 --> 00:05:16,860
to her?

73
00:05:17,340 --> 00:05:17,740
Of course.

74
00:05:18,780 --> 00:05:19,540
I do.

75
00:05:23,180 --> 00:05:24,140
To think

76
00:05:24,900 --> 00:05:26,860
your sister is so petty.

77
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:31,620
Not only that,

78
00:05:32,020 --> 00:05:33,340
if she finds out

79
00:05:33,620 --> 00:05:34,820
that you slept on her bed,

80
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:39,460
she would probably cry to me
like a baby.

81
00:05:42,940 --> 00:05:43,820
Besides,

82
00:05:46,820 --> 00:05:47,900
you have no idea.

83
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:55,740
That when my sister is angry

84
00:05:56,340 --> 00:05:58,460
and with her fierce face,

85
00:06:01,540 --> 00:06:02,340
she looks a bit ugly.

86
00:06:10,820 --> 00:06:11,740
It's getting late.

87
00:06:12,540 --> 00:06:13,580
I need to go back to the theater.

88
00:06:14,860 --> 00:06:15,540
If

89
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:18,180
I stay here for too long,

90
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,620
your sister will get mad

91
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:23,420
and turn ugly.

92
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:41,180
Shuangjiang has been slacking off
recently.

93
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:43,580
After he failed the task
in Qi City,

94
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:45,580
he stabbed the target

95
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:47,540
in his butts

96
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:49,260
and made him run two streets.

97
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:50,860
It was such a chaos.

98
00:06:51,660 --> 00:06:52,540
Find him back

99
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:53,420
and continue.

100
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:57,580
Qingming.

101
00:06:58,700 --> 00:06:59,220
Qingming!

102
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:01,420
Yes.

103
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:03,980
Is that so funny?

104
00:07:04,860 --> 00:07:05,500
No.

105
00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:08,100
You seem to be not in good form.

106
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:09,420
Go to Physician Ge

107
00:07:09,780 --> 00:07:11,500
to get yourself some calming medicine.

108
00:07:12,100 --> 00:07:12,700
You need more rest.

109
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:13,820
All right.

110
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:14,940
Thank you for your concern, sir.

111
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:22,220
Do you really want to move back?

112
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:23,420
Of course I'm going back.

113
00:07:23,540 --> 00:07:25,180
Otherwise, things might go wrong.

114
00:07:26,100 --> 00:07:26,860
It won't.

115
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:28,500
Haven't you realized this?

116
00:07:29,140 --> 00:07:31,180
I'm a genuine gentleman.

117
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:34,020
I like you, but I respect you.

118
00:07:34,740 --> 00:07:36,060
Before you accept me...

119
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:36,940
What are you talking about?

120
00:07:39,540 --> 00:07:40,780
Someone is going to take over my place

121
00:07:41,220 --> 00:07:42,460
if I don't go home now.

122
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:44,020
But this is not right.

123
00:07:44,660 --> 00:07:47,060
Why am I jealous of myself?

124
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:47,620
Mengchen.

125
00:07:47,620 --> 00:07:49,620
Er.

126
00:07:49,620 --> 00:07:50,500
I'm not making a thing of it.

127
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:51,540
Think about this.

128
00:07:52,020 --> 00:07:53,860
You went out
because you quarreled with your brother.

129
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:56,260
But Xiaosheng hasn't given out
any signs yet.

130
00:07:56,780 --> 00:07:57,860
If you go home now,

131
00:07:58,300 --> 00:07:59,580
you are giving in to him.

132
00:08:00,460 --> 00:08:01,140
You are right.

133
00:08:01,540 --> 00:08:03,340
If so, your position at home

134
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:06,780
will be vulnerable.

135
00:08:09,460 --> 00:08:11,420
No way.

136
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:15,540
But I can't just stay here.

137
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:16,980
If I don't go home...

138
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:19,260
Hold on. Wait.

139
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:22,540
Whatever I do isn't the right choice.
What should I do?

140
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:23,180
Let's go out for a stroll, then.

141
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:25,020
I don't want to.

142
00:08:25,460 --> 00:08:26,500
Leave me alone.

143
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:56,620
She is skilled in martial arts

144
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:58,100
and a good shooter.

145
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:00,740
I really don't have

146
00:09:01,580 --> 00:09:02,540
the measure of

147
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:04,740
the girl I have raised.

148
00:10:02,220 --> 00:10:02,940
Master.

149
00:10:03,740 --> 00:10:04,020
Brother.

150
00:10:04,260 --> 00:10:04,820
Patrolmen.

151
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:10,440
♪Evening breeze cradles verdant hills♪

152
00:10:13,460 --> 00:10:13,980
- Coach.
- Coach.

153
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:15,940
What are you doing here?

154
00:10:16,290 --> 00:10:17,450
We are on patrol under an order.

155
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:19,460
We came here to take a look
after hearing gunshots.

156
00:10:20,420 --> 00:10:21,220
I was practicing

157
00:10:21,660 --> 00:10:22,260
gun-shooting here.

158
00:10:26,140 --> 00:10:26,660
Why?

159
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:28,260
Do you want to ruin my mood?

160
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:29,820
Get lost.

161
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:37,010
♪Shielding the tiles from wind and rain♪

162
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:42,850
♪Garments swept over the flowing water,
pristine and clean♪

163
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:47,940
♪Swinging through autumn
to Stone Bridge Bay♪

164
00:10:48,820 --> 00:10:49,940
Are you not going home?

165
00:10:51,620 --> 00:10:52,300
No.

166
00:10:52,860 --> 00:10:53,500
I'm not going back.

167
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,300
Unless

168
00:10:55,580 --> 00:10:56,900
you hire eight bearers
to carry me home in a sedan chair.

169
00:10:59,020 --> 00:11:00,260
Silly girl.

170
00:11:01,060 --> 00:11:02,100
That's

171
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:03,460
for the marriage procession.

172
00:11:08,580 --> 00:11:09,420
Let's go home.

173
00:11:10,020 --> 00:11:10,540
Wait.

174
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:13,660
Don't you have any questions

175
00:11:14,060 --> 00:11:14,900
for me?

176
00:11:14,900 --> 00:11:20,500
♪A glance seals our fate♪

177
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:24,140
♪Without you, time fades into night♪

178
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:25,140
I used to think

179
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:28,460
you were the woman

180
00:11:28,980 --> 00:11:30,900
I wanted to protect for life.

181
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:33,700
♪My heart adrift,
seeking wings to break free♪

182
00:11:33,700 --> 00:11:34,820
But I didn't know

183
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:38,060
you are also Guyu,
who fights alongside me.

184
00:11:41,500 --> 00:11:42,500
As for why,

185
00:11:43,940 --> 00:11:44,860
I really want to know.

186
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,620
But I respect you.

187
00:11:47,260 --> 00:11:48,260
You can tell me

188
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:51,580
when you mean to.

189
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:58,420
Then do you prefer Guyu

190
00:11:58,980 --> 00:12:00,340
or Mengchen?

191
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:04,580
Well...

192
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:15,100
♪A glance seals our fate♪

193
00:12:16,130 --> 00:12:21,820
♪Without you, time fades into night♪

194
00:12:22,850 --> 00:12:28,410
♪My heart adrift,
seeking wings to break free♪

195
00:12:29,950 --> 00:12:34,810
♪Through tears, our love endures♪

196
00:12:35,450 --> 00:12:38,400
♪Fate entwined♪

197
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:41,150
♪Love and hatred intertwined♪

198
00:12:41,920 --> 00:12:44,030
♪My sorrow overwhelmed♪

199
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:48,130
♪I gaze at the moon, longing for you♪

200
00:12:48,580 --> 00:12:51,200
♪Love as vast as stars♪

201
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:55,490
♪In the galaxy,
I yearn for your presence♪

202
00:12:55,740 --> 00:13:04,260
♪In this fleeting dream,
love remains forever without regrets♪
